":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i0.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/001/134/657/452\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F001%2F134%2F657%2F452&h=065278b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c01f75ae95406a12e9e1a1339e8f11473c9aaf22","tid":410202,"uid":81852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:11:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"359cc00889e63e33ec85975bda99086954cafa42","tid":410202,"uid":53557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:21:49.000Z","msg":"講啲上面冇嘅<br />\n<br />\n佐助爭奪戰<br />\n鹿丸帶隊<br />\n逐個隊員留低對付相克技能嘅音忍四人眾<br />\n成套火影長治最型就係呢戰<br />\n寧次靠自身戰鬥力+智取都好深刻<br />\n<br />\n鹿丸係醫院自責個段睇到好心up<br />\n<br />\nps 好鍾意睇鹿丸分析對戰<br />\n次次都J死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dff2fa2e97348e5335bfd5adf40941e2598c8ce","tid":410202,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:24:45.000Z","msg":"出大玉螺旋丸果下最深刻<br />\n<br />\n乜修練完都係出螺旋丸 咁你練左d咩出黎"},{"pid":"9e00e179347bef7f9b020875b63dc465dd053f74","tid":410202,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:34:11.000Z","msg":"鋼手出場<br />\n個陣即刻搵H漫睇:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8454f4628ece0d7732c321d83e18dfb3d076200a","tid":410202,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:48:21.000Z","msg":"鋼手賭錢賭到輸身家要肉償嗰part"},{"pid":"2605be67ac3c96c2a961b2a928a5322e116c369e","tid":410202,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:56:20.000Z","msg":"自來也死同見到媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1327f1b865e6ab0803fbe53d6d4305a02c64d285","tid":410202,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:59:44.000Z","msg":"追佐助 下忍小隊同4人眾1打1"},{"pid":"39ce81d60a2ed6073d3c07162ed74f57bccec30d","tid":410202,"uid":47366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:04:17.000Z","msg":"分2part啦..<br />\n前期我覺得幾乎都完美..<br />\n中期就自來也&gt;鼬&gt;四代"},{"pid":"9f5a01ac58d4cc6edccff4168d7d484d223d0114","tid":410202,"uid":136119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:27:30.000Z","msg":"孖條<br />\n鼬死（穢土個次真死同打佐助個次都係）<br />\n綱手用一隻手指對鳴仔<br />\n四代既火影圍係到吹水傾計<br />\n鳴仔父母遺言<br />\n穢土轉生既水門問鳴仔小櫻係咪佢女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實仲有好多 不過即刻諗係諗到呢d先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3482871f96bb181b1c2473b8159957bc9171c38d","tid":410202,"uid":10644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:37:26.000Z","msg":"所有多由也有份出場嘅都好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://g1.addtext.ft-uc.com/MjAxNzA4MTY/addtext_com_MTM0MzUwMzc2NTY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg1.addtext.ft-uc.com%2FMjAxNzA4MTY%2Faddtext_com_MTM0MzUwMzc2NTY.png&h=0f0fa196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4947b9c4532996ef3daa2fe91b15e09d71914d48","tid":410202,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:42:43.000Z","msg":"最深刻都係雷切同千鳥<br />\n吵左十幾年 仲未分到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ecdbc888702563c6e6af431b34fcb7838ac4e0","tid":410202,"uid":15287,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T22:50:50.000Z","msg":"離題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望有人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.覺得作者寫得唔夠多小李<br />\n由最開頭小李vs 佐助 完勝佐助 證明努力係可以打贏天才 跟住打我愛羅 雖然輸咗 但當時佢可以話係木葉最強下忍 到君麻呂就開始輸 疾風傳更加係唔突出 後期體術/努力嘅戲份直頭畀晒凱 小李應該仲有好多發揮空間<br />\n2.寧次嘅死真係夾硬嚟 應該死嘅又唔死<br />\n自來也死應該係最好睇 阿斯瑪都還可以<br />\n寧次真係on9仔死法擋子彈死 純粹好似想喺忍界大戰整死一個配角然後一於揀寧次咁 <br />\n然後凱開八門 明明開八門有死嘅覺悟又為體術犧牲係幾撚熱血嘅事 直頭係真男人嘅浪漫<br />\n最後唔死真係抺殺咗種感覺<br />\n3.鳴人同雛田嘅感情好似寫得唔夠咁<br />\n印象中嗚人喺學風遁之前集集都喺度sakura醬 sakura 醬 根本對雛田冇感覺 然後到雛田命都唔要表白可能感動鳴人 但之後都未講有咩感情進展 連後期四代定唔知佢老母都問小櫻係咪你女朋友 最後冇啦啦又會娶雛田 好似驚死冇女要咁<br />\n佐櫻又係 明明佐助懶係浪子咁唔溝女 最後又中出小櫻唔要個女周圍去遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過你話為咗延續宇智波血脈都得嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c3906e42a32d7f67ff0e05840285a0a5841a6a","tid":410202,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T23:12:32.000Z","msg":"嗚人囉住孖條流眼淚"}]}